A Home Affairs Immigrations official was caught on camera busy on Whatsapp when she was supposed to be paying attention to stamping people's passports Home Affairs Minister Malusi Gigaba has expressed his disappointment on the situation and expects action to be taken by the department. “I was this morning informed about the video circulating on social media platforms, and have asked the Department of Home Affairs to investigate this matter and take swift action against the official,” says Gigaba. READ MORE: Home Affairs officials return to ANN7 studios, arrest 4 [WATCH] 